 salmon fillets onto Varoma tray. Drizzle 1-2 tablespoons of the reserved ginger sauce over salmon. Arrange zucchini and broccolini around salmon in Varoma, then secure Varoma lid and cook <b>6 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Arrange bok choy around salmon and other vegetables in Varoma, then secure Varoma lid and cook <b>5-7 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>, or until salmon and vegetables are cooked to your liking."},{"content":"Drizzle remaining ginger sauce over salmon and greens, then sprinkle with spiced cashews and serve immediately."}],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","30m","4 portions"]}